{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Cease sale and export of all UK-made arms to other countries",
        "additional_details": "The UK must stop the exportation, trading/ bartering and sale of all arms, ammunition and military vehicles to all countries around the world.\r\n \r\nThe sale of UK-made arms, ammunition and military vehicles to the UK\u2019s military should be the only exemption from this proposed rule- meaning UK-made weapons can be sold to the UK\u2019s military.\r\n \r\nHowever the UK\u2019s military (including all UK military personnel) must not give, sell, trade/barter or export arms, ammunition and military vehicles to other nations and organisations.\r\n \r\nToo many arms have been sold already, help stop the sale of weapons by signing this petition.",
        "background": "The UK is the second largest exporter of arms in the world. Arms made in the UK should not be used to cause damage and destruction across the globe.",
